data.description: New roof Dec 2023. BRING YOUR HORSES, LIVESTOCK AND HOBBY PROJECTS! 5 ACRES + a cozy home in Fort Worth for less than $425!!! Located just South of Benbrook Lake and less than 30 minutes from Downtown Fort Worth and Downtown Granbury via Chisholm Trail Parkway and Highway 377, enjoy the privacy of your land and the taste of the country life without giving up easy convenience and access to city attractions. This home features an open, inviting, split floor plan with lots of natural light all new laminate flooring throughout. Be ready to enjoy those Texas sunrises and sunsets from your front and back porches! The newly framed 40 X 60 steel on slab shop has a 15 foot opening for an RV and is stubbed for electric and water. The acreage is very usable with consistent grade and 2 heavily treed boundary fence lines for additional privacy. Bring your creativity. This property needs some TLC, but it has so much potential and opportunity to make your own!
